例年に引き続き、経済産業省後援下の開催となり、スポンサー企業やパートナーとしての協賛は約70社でした。<br><br>セッションやパネルディスカッション、ブースや交流会への参加など様々な特典がございます。","title":"2."},{"cover":"/assets/studio-design-asset-files/projects/RQqJk5Zag0/s-1000x583_v-fs_webp_55ba1e39-01a7-4abb-b98c-e54699117f5e.png","text1":"20校以上の大学機関と連携","text2":"例年、武蔵野美術大学、多摩美術大学を始めとした美大から、九州大学、近畿大学、千葉工業大学などの総合大学等を含めて約20校と提携し、デザイナー志望の学生100名以上の参加があります。<br><br>また、スピーカーとして原研哉氏や佐藤卓氏、田川欣哉氏や菅野薫氏、山中俊治氏らにもご登壇いただき、デザイナー向けの教育コンテンツとしても好評の声をいただいております。","title":"3."}]},"style":{"gap":"64px 0px","margin":"0px 0px 64px 0px","padding":"10px"},"tagName":"ul","type":"list","uuid":"c2ac70a1-e211-4529-b6df-9aa8ea62e9c2"},{"children":[{"children":[{"content":{"data":"資料請求する","type":"text"},"name":"資料請求ページへ","style":{"@mobile":{"fontSize":"15px"},"@tablet":{"fontSize":"18px"},"color":"#FFFFFF","fontFamily":"var(--s-font-3a8a8356)","fontSize":"23px","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","height":"auto","letterSpacing":"0em","lineHeight":"1","margin":"0px","textAlign":"center","width":"auto"},"uuid":"4e48728f-e2ae-49f8-8b1a-47b0abfa3146","children":[]}],"link":{"newTab":true,"path":"https://designshipjp.notion.site/2d2918173e3381a8989ed9bf6c365ed1?pvs=105"},"name":"Rectangle 21","style":{":hover":{"background":"#b90069ff","transitionDuration":"100ms","transitionTimingFunction":"ease-in-out"},"alignItems":"center","background":"#D22386","borderRadius":"150px","flexDirection":"row","flexWrap":"nowrap","gap":"0px 8px","height":"auto","justifyContent":"center","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","padding":"19px 39px 22px 40px","width":"290px"},"uuid":"372debcf-fc57-43c7-9f90-2828a6205cac"},{"children":[{"content":{"data":"お問い合わせは sponsor@design-ship.jp まで","type":"text"},"name":"Text","style":{"color":"#FFFFFF","fontFamily":"Montserrat","fontSize":"14px","fontWeight":600,"height":"auto","lineHeight":"1.4","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","textAlign":"center","textDecoration":"none","width":"auto"},"tagName":"","uuid":"f617f4b8-4a60-4e9f-9005-734243b05ed0","children":[]}],"name":"Box","style"